<li><p><m>h(x) = (x + 3)^{3}</m> c) <m>h(x) = \frac{1}{x} + 6</m></p></li>
<li><p><m>h(x) = \sqrt{5x - 3}</m> d) <m>h(x) = \frac{1}{x + 6}</m></p></li>
</ol>
